name: Admyral
headline: AI Agents to Automate Operations for Commercial Real Estate
description:
Admyral builds AI Agents to automate operations for the 143,000 commercial real estate brokers in the US.
Our first product is an agentic lead generation tool for commercial real estate brokers. We take a property address and use AI Agents to find the owner's contact details. Our deep agentic search beats the industry standard of 40% and is improving daily.

founders.name: Christopher Grittner, Founder
founders.description: Co-founder and CEO at Admyral. Prev led Philippines expansion at Finantier (YC W21), built Tacto's product from scratch as employee #4 (backed by Sequoia and Index), and led product initiatives at Celonis (valued at $13bn). Former Investment Team member at Earlybird Venture Capital. Researched LLMs in Data Analytics at University of Cambridge. BS in Computer Science & Business from Technical University of Munich and studied at National University of Singapore.

founders.name: Daniel Grittner, Founder
founders.description: Co-Founder and CTO at Admyral. Previously SDE at Amazon, published first-author computer vision research at ECCV 2022 while at TUM, and built database infrastructure at Celonis. Completed research project in Bioinformatics at ETH Zurich. BS in Computer Science from Technical University of Munich. Dropped out of MS in Computer Science at Technical University of Munich to build Admyral.

### Admyral: Revolutionizing Lead Generation in Commercial Real Estate

**Founded**: 2024

---

#### Mission
Admyral aims to empower the 143,000 commercial real estate brokers in the US by utilizing AI Agents to automate their operational tasks, specifically in lead generation.

#### Product Overview
Admyral's flagship product is an AI-driven **skip tracing tool** designed specifically for commercial real estate brokers. By simply inputting a property address, brokers can discover the owner's contact information within a minute, which vastly accelerates the tedious process of lead generation.

#### Key Features
- **Unmatched Efficiency**: Admyral boasts a lead generation accuracy that outperforms traditional methods, achieving a success rate of over 40%, and this is continuously improving.
- **Time Savings**: Brokers report saving about 40% of the time they previously spent on research.
- **Lead Generation Boost**: Users can potentially increase their outreach capacity by up to 4 times, leading to a staggering 96% client satisfaction rate.

#### How It Works
1. **Enter the Address**: Input the property's address into the platform.
2. **Retrieve Owner Details**: The AI processes the information and retrieves the owner's contact details.
3. **Engage and Convert**: Brokers can then reach out to the owners and secure listings without the cumbersome legwork that was once required.

#### Pricing
- **Pro Plan**: $149/month per seat for 50 skip traces per month, with unlimited users and founder support. A 7-day free trial is available.
- **Firm License**: Custom pricing based on specific needs, offering enterprise features and priority support.

#### Testimonials
Admyral has received positive feedback from numerous brokers who have experienced significant time savings and enhanced lead generation capabilities thanks to the tool. Users report doubling their outreach and reducing the time spent on research by as much as 2 hours a day.

---

**Admyral** is positioned at the intersection of AI and real estate, providing an invaluable resource for commercial brokers seeking to streamline their operations and boost their productivity. If you are in the commercial real estate arena and looking to supercharge your lead generation efforts, it’s worth checking out what Admyral has to offer.
